Mersheimer and Walt explain, prominent officials in the Bush administration included Paul

23:56.320 --> 24:00.720
Wolfowitz and Douglas Spieth, the number two and three civilians in the Pentagon,

24:00.720 --> 24:06.560
Richard Perl, Kenneth Adelman and James Woolsey, members of the Influential Defense Policy Board,

24:06.560 --> 24:11.360
Scooter Libby, the Vice President's Chief of Staff and National Security Advisor,

24:11.360 --> 24:15.680
John Bolton, Under Secretary of State for Arms Control and International Security,

24:15.680 --> 24:20.880
