27:18.000 --> 27:23.280
that reflects the union of our values and our national interests. Our comprehensive strategy

27:23.280 --> 27:31.200
to combat WMD includes proactive counter-proliferation efforts. We must deter and defend against the

27:31.200 --> 27:40.240
threat before it is unleashed. There's also the year 1996, when Richard Perle, Douglas Feith,

27:40.240 --> 27:45.760
