34:21.280 --> 34:26.160
Bush, and Condoleezza Rice to invade Iraq are all the more apparent by the fact that

34:26.160 --> 34:31.520
prior to September 11, there was no such commitment among them. Only nine days after

34:31.520 --> 34:36.560
the 9-11 attacks, The New York Times reported a split over the scope of retaliation.

34:37.440 --> 34:41.280
Some senior administration officials, led by Paul D. Wolfowitz,

34:41.280 --> 34:47.360
Deputy Secretary of Defense, and I. Lewis Libby, Chief of Staff to Vice President Dick Cheney,

34:47.360 --> 34:51.200
are pressing for the earliest and broadest military campaign against

34:51.200 --> 34:54.240
not only the Osama Bin Laden network in Afghanistan,

34:54.240 --> 34:59.440
but also against other suspected terrorist bases in Iraq and in Lebanon's Beqa region.

35:00.240 --> 35:05.280
These officials are seeking to include Iraq on the target list with the aim of toppling

35:05.280 --> 35:11.040
President Saddam Hussein, a step long advocated by conservatives who support Mr. Bush.

35:12.000 --> 35:16.400
A number of conservatives circulated a new letter today, calling on the president to make

35:16.400 --> 35:21.760
a determined effort to remove Saddam Hussein from power, even if he cannot be linked to the

35:21.760 --> 35:27.600
terrorists who struck New York and Washington last week. On Sunday, Vice President Dick Cheney

35:27.600 --> 35:32.640
seemed to ally himself with Secretary Powell's view when he said in a televised interview that

35:32.640 --> 35:38.080
the administration did not have evidence linking Saddam Hussein to last week's attacks. But Mr.

35:38.080 --> 35:43.440
Wolfowitz, the Pentagon's influential deputy secretary, is a conservative thinker who has

35:43.440 --> 35:48.320
frequently clashed with Secretary Powell and the State Department. He has continued to press for a

35:48.320 --> 35:52.960
military campaign against Iraq that would not only punish Mr. Hussein for his past support for

35:52.960 --> 35:58.560
terrorism at home and abroad, but would also eliminate the danger he poses to Israel and the

35:58.560 --> 36:06.000
West in his quest to acquire weapons of mass destruction. What went into flipping Vice President

36:06.000 --> 36:12.240
Cheney now considered one of the chief architects of the war? Mersheimer and Walt looked to his chief

36:12.240 --> 36:18.240
of staff. A key part of the public relations campaign to win support for invading Iraq was the

36:18.240 --> 36:22.800
manipulation of intelligence information in order to make Saddam look like an imminent threat.

36:23.600 --> 36:26.720
Scooter Libby was an important player in this endeavor.

36:28.240 --> 36:32.640
One need only look at the Plame Affair to see the quality of this intelligence,

36:32.640 --> 36:36.320
the sludge which sloshed around Washington in the lead-up to the war.

36:38.400 --> 36:43.920
