37:48.640 --> 37:55.520
and striking fact. The CIA had recently received intelligence showing that between 1999 and 2001,

37:55.520 --> 38:01.360
Iraq had attempted to buy 500 tons of uranium oxide from Niger, one of the world's largest

38:01.360 --> 38:08.480
producers, known as Yellow Cake. Two weeks later, the resolution passed overwhelmingly,

38:08.560 --> 38:12.560
giving the President a congressional mandate for a military assault on Iraq.

38:13.600 --> 38:18.400
A former high-level intelligence official told me that the information on Niger was judged

38:18.400 --> 38:23.360
serious enough to include in the President's daily brief, known as the PDB,

38:23.360 --> 38:26.400
one of the most sensitive intelligence documents in the American system.

38:27.040 --> 38:32.640
