III. I'm not suggesting sending 100,000 Marines, but there are plenty of Iranian targets. I hope

41:09.200 --> 41:15.440
I'm wrong. As I've said before, the Israel lobby is a series, and attention should be given to the

41:15.440 --> 41:21.360
ambitions of the Israel lobby on a nation of 90 million people just to Iraq's East. With the

41:21.360 --> 41:29.680
rising popularity of the neoconservatives yet again, perhaps Iran is more deserving of attention

41:29.680 --> 41:37.120
than ever. That's for the next one. The insiders who helped define the Bush doctrine are determined

41:37.120 --> 41:43.600
to set a course that will remake America's role in the world. They believe the removal of Saddam

41:43.600 --> 41:53.520
Hussein is the first and necessary act of that new era. And that fateful decision to take the

41:53.520 --> 42:05.600
nation to war now rests with the President of the United States.

